	(22, 1, '2015-10-26 11:18:53', '2015-10-26 11:18:53', '[vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1455688028972{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text][metaslider id=2652][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row layout="boxed" el_class="margin-bottom-15"][vc_column][cortana_heading title_style="no-border" font_size_title="20"][vc_basic_grid post_type="services" max_items="8" style="load-more" items_per_page="8" element_width="3" order="ASC" grid_id="vc_gid:1502799046918-6031c8c6-0562-5" el_class="insurance_box" btn_add_icon="true"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row layout="boxed"][vc_column][cortana_heading title="Welcome to AllKind Insurance" font_size_title="20"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_single_image image="2538" alignment="center"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="frnt_hdng" width="3/4"][vc_column_text]AllKind Insurance is an independent insurance brokerage. Insurance is beyond the matter of price which is why we are proud to offer our clients of the comprehensive insurance solutions as per their needs.\r\n\r\nWhether you need assistance with Personal, Business, Life, or Investments we have the experienced brokers to deliver the right product and services to satisfy your unique insurance requirements.[/vc_column_text][vc_raw_html]JTNDJTJGYnIlM0UlM0MlMkZiciUzRQ==[/vc_raw_html][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="custom-home-section">\r\n\r\nInsurance is an important part of Life. Our life is full of risk. Every day we go out for some work may not return home at the end of the day. Mishaps and accidents are quite common. But, if you have dependents at home, how would they survive without you? Did you ever think about this fact? We at All kind Insurance know realize this fact. We deal with wide range of products ranging from travel insurance, medical insurance till accidental insurance cover. We have a full range of insurance products that widely fulfills your desire.<strong>Types of insurance we cover</strong>\r\n\r\nUnlike other insurance companies who have only few products, we deal with a wide range of variations. You may not even be able to guess the extent of insurance that we provide to our clients. Following are some of the services:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Life insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Disability insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance for critical illness</li>\r\n	<li>Visitors health insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Travel insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Child education insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Travel insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Mortgage insurance etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Super Visa insurance</strong>\r\n\r\nThis is one of the unique variations of insurance provided by All kind Insurance. You may hardly discover this type of insurance in any other insurance company. This is for the elder family members of Canadian citizen. There are many couples working and staying in Canada. They have received the Canadian citizenship. But, their parents are grand parents may not stay in Canada. But, they wish to see their children out in Canada. The Super Visa insurance is the facility for those parents and grandparents. This will cover the health and hospitalization. You dont need to pay huge premium for this. This insurance can be valid for 2 years.\r\n\r\nYou can now visit our website and fill up an online form. Mention the plan, name, country, email, address and other details. You can even call us anytime for any type of insurance need.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<iframe style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/page.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsimransainiinsuranceadvisior%2F&amp;tabs=timeline&amp;width=340&amp;height=500&amp;small_header=false&amp;adapt_container_width=true&amp;hide_cover=false&amp;show_facepile=true&amp;appId=131294174150833" width="340" height="500" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Homepage 06', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'homepage-06', '', '', '2018-07-03 21:25:22', '2018-07-03 21:25:22', '', 0, 'http://www.cortana.osthemes.biz/?page_id=22', 0, 'page', '', 0),
