/h3>\r\naaxel uPVC material; do not support combustion, in fact they are self extinguishing. Throughout their product life, the material will not cause, support or enhance the natural development of fire. The profile compound possesses a fire retanrdant rating according to DIN 4 102, also fulfils class 1 fire resistance as defined in BS 476: part 7.[/vc_column_text][cortana_button link="url:%23|title:READ%20MORE|"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Longetivity</h3>\r\naaxel uPVC profiles maintain excellent inherent material properties. The windows and doors are attractive, perfactly tight and working well even after many years in use. The longevity and superior quality of this material has been conclusively proven over 30 years.[/vc_column_text][cortana_button link="url:%23|title:READ%20MORE|"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>High Acoustic/Sound Insulation</h3>\r\nThe Protection against noise is an essential characteristic of a modern window, in order to ensure comfortable life both at home and in office. aaxel uPVC windows and doors insulates up to 40 db which comes up to the German DIN standard for sound insulation Class 5,DIN 4109.[/vc_column_text][cortana_button link="url:%23|title:READ%20MORE|"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1455112399736{margin-top: 40px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_row_inner layout="boxed"][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 class="cortana-title border-bottom">WINDOW MAGIC CLIENTELE</h3>\r\n[cortana_partner_carousel layout_style="style2" images="749,748,747,746,745,744" column="6" autoplay="yes" img_size="full"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1446007130952{border-top-width: 1px !important;border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 65px !important;padding-bottom: 35px !important;background-color: #f9f9f9 !important;border