D%20MORE|"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="ameba_wrapper_content" width="1/3"][vc_column_text el_class="ameba_wrapper_inner_content"]\r\n<h3>High Acoustic/Sound Insulation</h3>\r\nThe Protection against noise is an essential characteristic of a modern window, in order to ensure comfortable life both at home and in office. aaxel uPVC windows and doors insulates up to 40 db which comes up to the German DIN standard for sound insulation Class 5,DIN 4109.[/vc_column_text][cortana_button link="url:%23|title:READ%20MORE|"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1455256274153{margin-top: 40px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}" el_class="top_class_window_magic"][vc_column][vc_row_inner layout="boxed"][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 class="cortana-title border-bottom">WINDOW MAGIC CLIENTELE</h3>\r\n[cortana_partner_carousel layout_style="style2" images="749,748,747,746,745,744" column="6" autoplay="yes" img_size="full"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1455258692279{border-top-width: 1px !important;border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 35px !important;padding-bottom: 35px !important;}"][vc_column el_class="top_class_blog"][vc_row_inner layout="boxed"][vc_column_inner][cortana_post title="Blog" item_amount="3"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Homepage 06', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 14:43:40', '2016-02-15 14:43:40', '', 22, 'http://supervisa.tejassolutions.ca/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
