	(2368, 1, '2016-02-16 16:59:43', '2016-02-16 16:59:43', 'Business Insurance\r\nFor any business to get successful and continue to be successful it is important to have an independent, knowledgeable and dedicated Business Insurance broker on their side who have access to multiple Business Insurance companies.\r\n\r\nWe at Aaxel are Independent insurance brokers and are contracted with over 25 National and International Commercial Insurance companies which are financially sound and dedicated to service our valuable clients.\r\n\r\nWe specialized in Business Insurance. Our Commercial Insurance brokers are very courteous and competent & we have ongoing commercial insurance training to our brokers. Business Insurance is very important line of business in our business. we have adequate resources allocated for our Commercial Insurance department and hence our Commercial Insurance programs are unmatchable.\r\n\r\nWe offer complete line of business overages including but not limited to Auto, Cargo, Commercial general liability (CGL) , Commercial property, Crime coverage, boiler and machinery (Equipment breakdown), business interruption, professional liability (E& O) , Directors and officers liability (D&O) etc.\r\n\r\nWe serve all industries including but not limited to: Manufacturing, Wholesale & Distribution, Hospitality, Contractors, Reality, Transportation, IT, Garages, retail and services industry.\r\n\r\nWhat else you looking for from a Business Insurance broker? Feel free to contact our commercial insurance department at 1-866-358-2860 or email  Contact us.\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>"A proper plan of insurance does not cost - it saves!"  </b>', 'Business Insurance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2331-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-16 16:59:43', '2016-02-16 16:59:43', '', 2331, 'http://supervisa.tejassolutions.ca/2331-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
